      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so pointless lately. like every time i turn on the news or even just look outside, it's the same thing. everything is just breaking down. how are people even supposed to find a reason to keep going when the planet is literally dying? it feels like we're just watching the end of everything in slow motion.",
